nobody is probably going to read this crap but if i don't talk to someone - machine or otherwise - right now i may very possibly explode.  or maybe implode...that would be cooler to see.  wait...i probably couldn't see myself imploding could i.  damn.  another sucky thing to happen today!  rock on sucking!!!

so yeah...tonight seriously kicked my ass.  first of all i sat on my couch for 3 hours playing some damn computer game.  how worthless am i??  then i get a call from my boyfriend's FRIEND telling me he forced my boyfriend to go to the bar with him.  bullshit he was forced.  a chance to go out and drink?  whyever would he refuse?? he couldn't even call me himself...but had to make his friend lie for him.  that made me feel really good about myself.  especially since it's the exact same thing my ex used to do to me so he could go out and drink and chase tail all night long.  so now i'm reliving all of that HORRIBLE relationship and i'm soooo pissed that i'm being forced to deal with it again with a whole new boyfriend that i didn't think would treat me like this.  
so there i was practically in tears because i'm seeing my relationship go horribly wrong just like my last one did (so maybe i'm over-reacting but if you knew what my ex put me through you would understand why i'm freaking out - yes it was THAT bad...)...so i decided to go take a shower to calm down or occupy my brain or something.  10 minutes later i emerge from the shower to find that the dogs have ripped open a trash bag and it's contents are strewn all over my apartment.  so i got to spend the next wonderful half hour cleaning up all that shit.  it was fucking awesome let me tell you!  
then the evening started to improve!  miraculous!  my friend jeff called me and asked if i wanted to go to a little get-together and drink some beers with him since he's leaving next week.  fucking alright! so now i'm just waiting for him to call me back so he can tell me how to get to wherever we're going.  
so hopefully that will happen soon and i can go have some fun and forget about all this bullshit for awhile.  

is it my damn birthday yet?

so i have 3 days of school left.  that is very neat.  i went and did my "exit interview" for financial aid.  that was pretty dumb.  since i'm coming back for the bachelor's in october my loans get deferred more...that means i have to go to the sallie mae  website and print off some form and take it in to financial aid and get it certified and send it in.  good times right?!?!?!  BUT...i have 6 months in which to accomplish this irritating task, so i'm not too concerned at this point.  
i am concerned that my parents will be here 1 week from today...i need to start cleanin this apartment!!!  ooo...i also need to figure out the fastest/easiest/cheapest (or something) route to st. augustine since they want to go there for some reason.  i have a feeling that will be a long week...st. augustine...disney...nagging...blah...
at least i have this weekend to have fun : )

ooo i should post pics of my new puppy!   i think i will do that next!!  she is cute!

i hate workstations.  i want to kill the teacher.  
so nothing has changed since before spring break.
today we're learning about MIDI....oh joy.  we had a whole month on MIDI before this so i really don't think the teacher needs to go into everything quite so deeply.  it is zero fun.  but yeah...such is the nature of the class.  
and i have lab afterwards.  BURN!  
this weekend was fun though.  saturday rocked.  poor dug...he got some nasty things drawn on him again.  guess he shouldn't pass out before everyone else.  hehehehehe.
i need to clean my room.  maybe i'll do that tonight.  i should just go get some boxes and start packing stuff.  then maybe i'd be able to keep my floor visible.  probably not, but it was a nice idea.  i need to start looking at apartments and figure out where the hell we're moving to.  maybe kortni and i can go tour some places this week or next week.  that would be neat.  too bad all the really cool places are so damn far away from school.  now would be a good time to invent a teleporter.  someone should get on that pronto.  
i wonder how andrea's issues worked out last night.  maybe i should have stayed up.  i'm glad i went with my boyfriend on spring break so he had no way to cheat on me.  not that he would...but it sucks to think about it no matter what.  especially in her situation.  i would be pissed.  
so yeah...guess i better start paying attention or something.

if anyone wants a dog there was a rottweiler chillin in the chick fil-a parking lot.  i wanted to take him home but he might eat rilo.  and that would be icky.

it's 6:17am and i am hangin out at orlando international waiting for my 7:55am flight to columbus.  there's a little food booth thingy across the hall and the people working apparently don't know how the fuck to cook cuz it's all smokey and smells like burning.  fun fun fun fun times for meredith.  there's another flight leaving out of this gate at 7:00 so there's a bunch of people with cranky little kids chillin over here.  90% of them have mcdonald's bags and coffee.  i wonder where the mcdonalds is.  i could go for a bacon egg and cheese biscuit right about now.  this is going to be a long day.  i've been awake since 4pm yesterday.  woo hoo!!!  spring break!!!!
wow...there are a lot of people running around with big ass easter baskets.  hehehe.  the funny part is they're all over 40.  hope they have kids waiting for those somewhere.  i'm sitting in a very uncomfortable phone cubicle thing right now.  less personal then the chairs AND  i can plug in the powerbook.  the security dudes yelled at me cuz i forgot to take it out of my bag before i put it through the x-ray guy.  oh well.  fuck em.  i care not.  i would really like to go to sleep.  maybe i can sleep on the plane.  i hope it isn't too full.  it's open seating (which i've never experienced) so hopefully i'll get a row to myself.  or at least 2 seats.  but with my luck some big smelly fat dude will plop down beside me and overflow into my seat.  GRRRRRR.  i really hate travelling.

i can't believe we're having a lecture on the last day before spring break.  having a midterm was bad enough...but the way this lecture is going it's probably going to run late -AGAIN- and i just want to go home and sleep.  that would be neat.  damn...he's been talking about ONE point on a slide for 25 minutes!  and he's still going!  if i were in hell this would be in.  this fucker lecturing me about something retarded for all eternity.  i better start prayin or something.  i don't want to have that happen forever.  ick.
oh good.  now he's telling us about programs to download.  that's fucking great.  shut up bitch!  let us go home!   
at least last night was fun.  kortni and ryan and i hung out.  they got drunk and i made flash cards for this stupid midterm.  that reminds me...i have to give him money today.  crap.  better write it on my hand.  wait it's there already!  sweet!  maybe the ATM will be working.  i would be excited.  i should probably get some money for the trip too.  don't like to travel with zero dollars.  is it sunday yet?  i would be very happy.  i'm ready to get far away from school for a few days.  this place is making  me crazy!  i love it...but it's making me crazy!
man...i really have to pee.  maybe we'll take a break soon.  i think we should just skip the break and leave early.  but out teacher the coffee fiend probably won't let that happen.  grrrrrrr.
alright...this dude needs to quit showing us plug-ins from the digidesign website and get on with the damn lecture!   we don't care!  we can look at this crap on our own time!  i hate you teacher!   aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaahhhh!!!!!!!!!!!  OH MY GOD I AM GOING TO FUCKING KILL HIM
someone make it end!!!!!!!!!!
this is just getting ridiculous.  we've been sitting here for over an hour and we've been through 3 slides.  and i'm sure there are a LOT more.  no way we're getting out on time.  well shit i should be used to that.  if we take a break i'm leaving.  i have 2 hours left to miss.  i may just have to use them.  i can't take this dousch anymore.  if i stay i might get violent.  seriously.  now he's bitching about people talking.  maybe he should take the hint that he needs to shut the fuck up and let us go.  but nooooo.  he just gives us a speech on how we need to respect "his" time in lecture.  fuck that.
i haven't been this pissed in awhile.  good thing i can type a post so i don't freak out and kill people or something.  that would probably not be too good.  i don't really want to go to jail.  that would suck.
GRRRR!!

so yeah i'm bored and i'm typing.  maybe i'll even remember to post it when i get home.  that would be neat.  alright!  now i'm deaf because my teacher finds it necessary to crank  up the speakers while he's doing a crappy drum edit!  this is just peachy!

so here i am sitting in class waiting to start.  good thing i brought the powerbook!  gives me something to occupy my time with.  i think i've gone insane.  last night i went to sleep at like 11 or so and i woke up at 12 and thought it was noon instead of midnight.  whoops.  luckily i figured it out and didn't try to go to lab.  that would have been funny.

...to be continued

so i spent the last 2 hours looking at my old yearbooks and my scrapbook from high school.  needless to say i'm pretty depressed now.  it's strange to see pictures of you and  your "old friends" having the times of your lives and realize that you'll probably never even see most of them again.  andrea gave me a picture of me and micheal tonight too...and that made me think of everything we went through together and how much i miss him.  i wish people didn't have to die.  at least not when they're 18 years old.  and when they have issues with others that they have yet to work out.  even though we spent a lot of time pretending to hate each other...i really did love him.  and he really loved me.  so much, in fact, that his last girlfriend hated me for it.  sometimes i wonder what might have been.  but so does everyone at one time or another.  what really hurts is that fact that i couldn't even go to his funeral.  that's something i'll regret forever i'm sure.  
then i started thinking about all the people that i was so close to for what is really such a short time.  it's so weird how you can love people soo much and then never talk to them again once high school ends and you start a new life, and they all forget about you.  and even if you do see them again, you know it can never, ever be the same.  
wow...i sound like a bitter pathetic asshole don't i?  well i don't give a shit at this point.  i need to get it out or something.
you know what's amazing?  it's amazing how much i've changed since high school.  even since i was 18.  it's like i'm a totally different person.  i'm not sure if that's better or worse...probably better.  i hope so anyway.

i guess my conclusion is that i'm very happy with my life now, and the people i'm surrounded by.  i'll always remember the good times, and the bad ones, but i shouldn't be too sad that they're over because i'll always have the memories, no matter what.  like our class motto said: "don't cry because it's over, smile because it happened."
that makes a lot of sense.

doodley doo...

i'm sleepy...again.  it's annoying.  it's like this month just made me constantly tired.  on friday i fell asleep at 7pm and didn't wake up untill almost 8 saturday morning.  it felt good to sleep that long though.  
played some drunken basketball on saturday night.  that was entertaining.  maybe i'll do it again soon.  got some great "action shots" with my phone.  i love it when people are so entertained by a camera that happens to be in a cell phone.  they're funny.
dug and i made some progress on the ep tonight.  i came up with a cool piano part.  it was pretty fun.  now i just need to sit down and work on the rest of the songs.  hopefully i can come up with something cool for them too.  
hmmm...think i'll watch some more mystery science theater 3000 (thanks baby!  i love it!)
